      "body": "我这边的issues 有两个问题。\r\n1 Textarea嵌套的滑动冲突问题。（0.9 已经修复）\r\n2 Textarea 初始化的时候内容高度>控件高度的时候不能滑动问题。场景如截图中评论被拒绝后，再次编辑！（0.9 未修复）\r\n\r\n我是在textarea中添加这块代码来解决的。\r\n    editText.addOnLayoutChangeListener(new View.OnLayoutChangeListener() {\r\n      @Override\r\n      public void onLayoutChange(View v, int left, int top, int right, int bottom, int oldLeft, int oldTop, int oldRight, int oldBottom) {\r\n        if (v.canScrollVertically(-1) || v.canScrollVertically(0)) {\r\n          EditText view = (EditText) v;\r\n          if (view.getMovementMethod() == null) {\r\n            view.setMovementMethod(ArrowKeyMovementMethod.getInstance());\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n对WXEditText 中\r\nif(h < contentH){\r\nsetMovementMethod(null);\r\n}不清楚为什么要这样设置？？\r\n\r\n![Uploading Screenshot_20161228-111757.jpg…]()\r\n![Uploading Screenshot_20161228-112058.jpg…]()\r\n![Uploading Screenshot_20161228-112355.jpg…]()\r\n"
    }
  ],
  "created_at": "2016-12-13T03:54:05Z",
